ISLAMABAD, May 19 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi on Thursday urged the need for accelerated efforts to develop intellectual capabilities in the field of emerging technologies such as Artificial Intelligence, Quantum Computing, Data Analysis, Cyber Security and Space Technology to increase the pace of national development.
He made these remarks while talking to the participants of the Senior Officer Leadership Course, at Aiwan-e-Sadr.
